Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.74,0:00:11.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,猛烈的雨令心頭震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.54,0:00:16.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,像那日一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.35,0:00:22.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,直至昨日我一直追逐着的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.54,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在仍然相信它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.59,0:00:34.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,沒終結的防衛也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.20,0:00:42.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你繼續凝望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VICTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.37,0:00:50.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,迎接過不知多少個早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,將來一定會抓緊給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VICTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.49,0:01:02.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,即使甚麽也沒有都不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.06,0:01:14.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要懷着沒人能代替的你的笑臉

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.11,0:01:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索能打退格諾古因他小心謹慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.82,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因為有地利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但今後大人們的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.09,0:01:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非在卡沙尼里亞進行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.23,0:01:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，胡索被捲入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險的戰爭去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂的心底很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.73,0:01:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛索拿的反擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！胡索！你是個天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，奧迪羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，艾賓 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要玩到幾時呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要解除V模式搬入去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.76,0:02:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，你說在解除V模式…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，用分體指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為分體還是第一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說，在戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我結合嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們相信你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這班是甚麽人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放那個下來就行了，尼昂列度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅，在那裡回收下身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下身部份？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.49,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是站着那部份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站着？真的在站着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅 好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡美昂由我來控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素芝你也來幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是年青機師駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去機庫接他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙駕駛的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡來的呀！？真的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是你在戰斗嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過啦，機師是很年青的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是個小學生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人一邊看着你的戰斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊進入這工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們沒想過駕駛的是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有支援你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒有多謝我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種謙虛的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能令人的關係改進的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂…在哪裡呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和卡魯曼在散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.82,0:04:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年青人們張開夢想的翅膀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何那女孩懂姐姐所唱的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何那女孩和嬰兒總是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我要去的地方前面出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緣份真奇怪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加里，丹少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我止痛藥，我還能好好戰斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那裡的哪一個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最前面那個，我不管了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡說格諾古中尉還生存…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是結果論！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加里少尉向我出示單獨出擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,批文，然後向葛索拿的倉庫去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有必要去看看情況了\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要橫蠻無理！加里\N丹少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛索拿才剛剛組合完畢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠動就行了！少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這機體何時出動試驗呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止！加里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那身體別勉強呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要受審也沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我替沙伯特報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制止加里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果戀人被殺，就會變得瘋狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨比任何武器更能發揮力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫達利，你也認為如果看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加里和白色動戰士接觸之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗起來就會更容易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,納普尼！出動機動堡壘列卡路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不洩露加里的行動之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行監視 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙伯特的仇，如果不是由我去報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由誰去報呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃多點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂和胡索在哪裡呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麽，我的操縱怎樣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像無受傷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪去別人生命的心情怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是甚麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能相信為何像你這樣的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做出那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是由於害怕而不由得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很普通的，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想做才去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是不要變成可怕人呢，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息的傳遞很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回去報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在前面攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可讓敵人知道所在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好像也很快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可讓他們那樣順利的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的秘密工場在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格諾古不像樣地還生存嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還未能用米諾基粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有間諜潛入來嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有很多小型車輛在躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格諾古自己會逃走的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所在一敗露就發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！要待他進入攻擊范圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只得一部機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只得一部新型機來嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,援軍有甚麽事呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒事吧！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒事！快逃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，雖然你還很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你再次出擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐，你傷勢又復發嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還未能出動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕吧，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那麽由誰去呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人民共和軍集合了，定有人在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了那班人戰斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不能去莎蒂，你沒所謂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子和這場戰爭是無關係的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相殘殺由大人們去做就夠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有要保護的東西才戰斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，只顧自己的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你別出聲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索只是個小孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐，我們對胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很大的期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很接近了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想卡迪珍娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐和大家死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…就是那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心…是很寶貴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們最想珍惜的心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過你不過是只顧自己罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，結合的程序你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核戰機準備出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核戰機的出發指示怎樣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為那能殺死沙伯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯勤炮和地面炮火也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦呢！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這班人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的痛楚我也要你們嘗一嘗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射上身部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！在紅色煙幕之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會發射上身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！去追上它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.01,0:11:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要發射了！發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那邊吸引了注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V模式指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？是大型機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小型機怎樣了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小型機在哪裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是北面出口的升降機前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射下身部份的時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逃脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為下身部份正用來牽制敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.95,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以請等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發射黃色的記號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索就會明白的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！發射記號彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎！古夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以發射！記號彈！黃色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何時發射！現在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是援軍嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！如果小型機也在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.91,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會被包圍的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加，美利迪亞所開發的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嗎？ 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.03,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它正在結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米諾基粒子已正式散佈了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉用本機的攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠這映象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝備的分析須要少少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫達利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲痛的效能看來很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為給予戰士葬身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是賞賜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部列卡路和葛索拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測試飛行資料也能得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密捷！回去基地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使變成機動戰士，雷射劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗我也不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上我斬傷那機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用血的顔色把那白色和藍色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士染成鮮紅吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索他又在戰斗嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會死的！不要死呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止你的動作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.90,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是平民造的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有 甚麽作為呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.25,0:14:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸給你的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完結了嗎？完結了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是機師！他在做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還未…還未完結的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是被一部機動戰士…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會像沙伯特般被打敗的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要來…不要來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他瘋了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭部的巴魯勤炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一兩發子彈剩下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.92,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我用它們，連你也會…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是加里.丹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的會發炮的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺光你們！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類憤怒的話就會變得瘋狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.76,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…全是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於你給予了敵人機師們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生很大的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的存在是很重要的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣敏感是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能那樣想的胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很好的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那種小孩捲入戰爭裡的你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種想法我沒有反對的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！但是！但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！世界中只有他嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們定會說，\N因為有很多原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要可以吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.96,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟去了哪裡呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，但是…真好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去卡沙尼里亞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做吧，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成莎蒂的說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…我會考慮一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於這裡已被卑斯柏發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能再有一該猶疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這工場的設備和機體要立即拆散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明早就由我們卡美昂隊來殿後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前大家順序離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心食物之後輪到這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次會去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大叔們走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，我們…胡索，睡着了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很倦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他慢慢睡到明早吧 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和斯納德隊的接觸怎樣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用無線電的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不縮短距離是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英國方面怎樣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵，要快點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為伯爵的是首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.76,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間不是那裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去DD地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和運輸機會合…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去洗手間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那雙眼我見過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快重新組合呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加，美利迪亞厲嵗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吃早餐前休息一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一輪才剛剛完畢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一的目標是要毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加，美利迪亞的工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員各就各位！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅美洛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼昂列度！胡索去牽制敵人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！不行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！你很怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕！但是不能就此死去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我默默等死！我不願！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道父母的事就死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂你也不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道父母的事就死去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伏低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快離開這裡 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素芝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.48,0:21:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有戰機注意
